Formosa Chairman Says Outlook ‘Very Bad,’ Daily Says

-- B y   A n d r e a   W o n g
-- 
2011-06-17T00:53:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-17/formosa-chairman-says-outlook-very-bad-daily-says-correct-.html
(Corrects the newspaper’s name in first paragraph.)  Taiwan’s petrochemical industry will
be hurt by competition from Singapore as well as tight monetary
policy in China, the Apple Daily cited Wilfred Wang, chairman of
 Formosa Petrochemical Corp. (6505)   Wang’s outlook for the industry in the second half of the
year is “very bad,” the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Wong in  Hong Kong  at 
 awong268@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
